FAQs

Medgic.pk is a glabal platform to provide healthcare services for men. Our platform allows men of all ages to get a fast, convenient and reliable health consultation discretely through our official website. We offer a panel of doctors and health concerns listed on the webpage, anyone from anywhere can take an assessment as per their health issue and our doctor expert provides a detailed and personalised health plan accordingly with regular follow-ups.

From Hair loss to sexual health issues. We pioneer in providing the best of health experts to assist you on your journey to betterment and recovery.

Currently, we are only offering Allopathic treatment which is prescribed as per individual diagnosis.

Medgic.pk provides reliability, dependability and smartest solutions via our list of all health experts along with their qualifications and experience in health care. Kindly, click here to view the list of experts now: Our Team

Medgic offers full access to our list of doctors’ history, qualifications & certifications to enable you to explore and consult a doctor only if you are satisfied.

All medical treatment involves certain level of side effects, however, side effects may vary individually. Our health experts are required to inform you of any likely side effects as per your prescribed medication. You may also reach out directly via our email follow-ups to consult if you feel any abnormality or symptoms upon consuming medication.

Kindly consult your relevant doctor via our follow-up emails to ask any personalised questions concerning your treatment.

Medgic’s services are provided by healthcare professionals to promote, maintain, or restore health. These health professionals are trained to help people address their health concerns and improve your quality of life. What sets us apart from a normal clinic or hospital is our smart approach to reach out our patients online.

Treatment course timeline varies patient to patient depending on their severity and conditions. Medgic never gives up on their patients until we are satisfied that you are feeling uplifted and healthy again!

Medicines prescribed by our health experts are readily available from your nearby pharmacy. We primarily rely on prescribing localised medications so that everyone can easily purchase them. If the medicine is not locally available or (in some cases) not suitable for your treatment then we may prescribe imported medicines to ensure your recovery.

Once you have submitted your assessment form, you will be contacted directly by our health expert via the email address you have provided in your assessment form.

We do not have a physical entity or clinic in Pakistan as yet. We are only accessible online. You may learn more about our services and health professionals on our website.
